      "practice": "Set a small candle in a holder on the table and place a small bowl or dish of salt beside it. Light the candle. Sit down and take time to settle fully into the moment. Take a few cleansing breaths. Lift your hands and place your fingers in the bowl of salt. Close your eyes and breathe deeply. As you exhale, visualize unwanted energy or the undesired emotion flowing down your arms, out through your fingers, and into the salt. Continue until the release feels complete enough for this sitting. Remove your fingers from the salt and open your eyes. Focus on the candle. Breathe in and visualize the warmth and brightness of the flame entering your body and filling it with light and beauty. Continue until refreshed enough to close. Extinguish the candle. Dissolve the salt in water and pour it down the sink.",
